    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.dE8h1C8gOUyzeS0J]{Epiphanies}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">&nbsp;When you cast a spell with a duration of longer than 1 round, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to double its duration. If the spell is one of your connection spells with a duration of 1 minute per level or longer, its duration increases to 24 hours instead. You can have only one spell affected by this epiphany at a time, and using this ability while another spell is already in effect causes that previous spell to immediately end as if its duration had expired.&nbsp;</span></p>",
